26 (3) SUBSTANTIAL DEVIATION FROM PLANS, SPECIFICATIONS, OR
27 REQUIREMENTS HAS OCCURRED OR IS ABOUT TO OCCUR;
28 (4) THE DEPARTMENT IS REFUSED ENTRY TO ANY PREMISES FOR
29 THE PURPOSE OF EVALUATING COMPLIANCE WITH THE RESERVOIR AUGMENTATION
30 PERMIT;

